If you are looking for a highly efficient, responsive and experienced FULL STACK software developer for a long term relationship, to take care of all your development needs, I am your guy. ► PROFICIENT software dev/design areas: ★ .Net (C#, VB.Net), ASP.net MVC 3,4,5 (Unity, NInject), T-SQL, MVC Web/Odata APIs, Owin Oauth, JWT, Web Forms, Java, WPF, Silverlight, DI. TDD ★ Kendo UI, Framework7, Angular.js, Knockout.js, ChartJS, DevExtreme, Prototype.js, JQuery, Javascript, HTML5, CSS3, Telerik Platform, Telerik App Builder ★ Dapper, Entity Framework (Code-First, Database First), XPO ★ Express Application Framework (XAF) and Express Persistent Objects (XPO) Expert, Business Objects design, UI customization, Reporting, Scheduler & Dashboards. ★ Telerik, DevExpress, Infragistics, Fluent (Reporting,Win,Web, WPF) 3rd party dev tools ★ MSSQL, MySQL, SQLLite, SQL Compact, MS Access. ★ Xamarin, Xamarin.Forms. Android, DevExtreme, PhoneJS, ChartJS, PhoneGap/Cordova Additionally I am an expert on : ★ Inversions of Control/Dependency Injection, TDD, MVVM, multi-layered architecture. ★ Source Control (Git) (Github, Bitbucket), Microsoft TFS, Tortoise SVN ★ XPath, JSON, XML, VBA, Office/Outlook APIs, Sharepoint API, Power BI API, PInvoke I take pride in strong debugging, re-factoring, problem solving skills with passion to solve complex business problems and delivering best & optimized solution for clients. Feel free to contact to know more about my work and how I can help you.

profiles.title: Mobile and Web development, native iOS & Android.
profiles.description:
Hello,  

I'm happy to represent interests of the Erminesoft LLC agency. 

Erminesoft LLC is the full stack software outsource company since 2012. We provide quality mobile and web development services (Native iOS and Android, ReactJS, PHP, HTML5, CSS, Javascript, AJAX, MySQL, Prototype, jQuery) as well as the design, project management, BA and QA.

Welcome to our dev center:

- Full-cycle development (from graphic design in layers to app submission)
- 30 days free support for projects with timeline 2-3 months
- Fluent English (both written and voice communications) 
- Strong background for the following industries: Real Estate, Games, chatting apps, e-learning and social networking as well as e-commerce on mobile.
- Strong ReactJS development team


Service Description

• Mobile - iOS (iPhone/iPad), Android), including Swift SDK
• Web - ReactJS, HTML5, CSS, Javascript
• Testing and QA
• Project management and requirements analysis

Services Description:

Mobile apps
1. Social app - iOS, Android
2. RealEstate apps - iOS, Android
3. Listing apps - iOS, Android
4. Delivery service - iOS, Android
5. Internal companies communication app - iOS, Android
6. GPS tracking app - iOS, Android
7. Business app - iOS, Android
8. Catalogue/Shopping cart app: iOS, Android
9. Barcodes reading Apps: iOS, Android
10. iBeacon apps
11. 2d games: iOS, Android

Other:
API REST, SOAP, Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, Google APIs, connection with SNs
Ad networks integrated: Mopub, Playhaven, Applovin, Vungle, Tapjoy, Mdotm

profiles.description:
✅ Top-Rated Web & Mobile Dev 
✅ Oracle certified 
✅ Trial job - 2 weeks
✅ Software architect with 10 years of experience
✅ Top UK and Belarus mobile development agency by clutch.co
✅ 70+ completed projects. 
✅ 100% job success rate on Upwork.
✅ Technical partnership: can solve all technical issues for startups. 

I’m Oracle Certified Professional and oDesk Verified Mobile Developer.  
I’ve 10 years of development experience in Java Enterprise and Android development. For now, I’m technical lead & solution architect at Smartum Pro. We are focused on native mobile apps and full-stack startup development.  The current team has been working together for 4 years and  has strong experience in:
 - Mobile development for iOS and Android
 - Java/Oracle enterprise solutions 
 - PHP (Symfony, Laravel, Yii) web development

Rates (It can be reduced in case of long term full-time allocation):
 - Senior-level engineer (5+ years) - $35;
 - Middle-level engineer (2+ years) - $20

We can offer risk-free period (trial job) for project and process setup. It means if you will not satisfied with a quality of our work you can terminate the contract without payment during the first 2 weeks of our collaboration.

A few more points to work with us:
 - Focus on quality of technical solution
 - Transparent process.
 - Reasonable rates
 - Available during US working hours  (overlap at least 4h per day)

Here you can find a list of delivered projects by the link smartum.pro/upwork. A big part of projects are covered by NDA, we can share a bit more information during the voice call.
Let’s talk! 

How can I contact you?

Look forward to productive collaboration,
Sergey V. 
CTO at Smartum Pro
